        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A comprehensive diesel generator service in Brisbane involves more than just a simple oil change or visual check. It requires a systematic approach to both mechanical and electrical components to ensure every part of the system integrates seamlessly during a power transition. Expert technicians use specialised diagnostic tools to measure performance metrics and identify wear patterns that might not be visible to the untrained eye."
